title: DVDFab Platinum 5.0.6.0 with Serial-SBA777
description:
DVDFab Platinum is the most powerful and flexible DVD copying/burning software. With 8 copy modes, you can back up any DVD to DVDR in just a few clicks.

DVDFab Platinum is brand new, is completely rewritten, is based on more than 6 years of DVD copy software development.

July 15, 2008 - DVDFab 5.0.6.0 Updated!

    * New: Added "DVDFab Video Decoder" and "DVDFab Audio Decoder" as default DirectShow decoder for Preview.
    * New: Added subpicture support for Preview. User can switch subpicture while playing now.
    * New: All UI options are memorized, so that user don&#039;t need adjust it every time.
    * New: Reduced time to open DVD in certain cases.
    * New: Update language files.
    * Fix: Rollback VSO burning engine since the latest one has bugs.
    * Fix: DVD created by some DVD recorders can&#039;t be opened.
    * Fix: Audio volume in Preview cannot be adjusted.
    * Fix: A crash problem at DVDFab startup in certain cases.
    * Fix: Several crash problems when opening DVD in certain cases.
    * Fix: A crash problem when analyzing DVD title in certain cases. (DVDFab Mobile Option)
    * Fix: Several minor problems.
